The name is about wave interference pattern, used to make the logo in spawn and the portals textures. The theme revolves around a castle-like triangulated world. Has some dynamic triangles effects.
That's all i guess.

BTW AFAIK that's the first map that uses 1+ non-parallaxing skyboxes. I guess that must be true as I've never seen proper multiple skyboxes before.
